AB  - Digital transformation is driving the overall change of production, life style and governance. During the 14th Five-Year Plan period, Yibin will focus on building a smart logistics platform and a smart port development zone, and promote the development of urban digital construction by strengthening the integration of smart logistics and manufacturing industries. In the context of digital transformation of the city, frstly this paper summarizes the current situation of the research on the synergy between the two industries at home and abroad, then qualitatively analyzes the current situation and characteristics of the development of the two industries in Yibin, then uses the composite system model and DEA model to gradually and quantitatively analyze the degree of synergy and synergy efciency of the two industries, and fnally puts forward relevant countermeasures and suggestions to improve the service level of the logistics industry and the competitiveness of manufacturing enterprises in Yibin, and Yibin will be an innovative modern industrial cluster, actively strive to become a national demonstration base on intelligent terminal industry, and at last become a demonstration city of intelligent terminal application in China.  © 2021 Copyright held by the owner/author(s). Publication rights licensed to ACM.
